This paper is about developing a conversational agent that can perform multimodal search-based dialogue. The paper uses neural response generation and a knowledge base to improve the performance of the model. Given this, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and computational linguistics. Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
